overview: Is that a pistol in his pocket, or is Magnum just glad to see you? Find out in this bawdy and bizarre series, dedicated to the principle that no guy likes going off half-cocked!  Includes four classic scenes: "Johnny and Skipper" starring Johnny and Skipper,  "Take a Chance" starring Paul Strand and Greg Kolb,  "Room Service" starring Dennis Johnson and Steve Boyd, "The Ranch Dudes" starring Jack Wrangler and Biff.
title: Magnum Griffin Collection: Volume 5
